sources.title: I Wonder Who's Killing Her Now? 1975 (Crime, Comedy) Bob Dishy, Joanna Barnes | Movie
sources.description:
Oliver is in trouble. He's been caught embezzling money from his father's company, and unless he can pay back the $250,000 he took (which he can't), he will be fired from his job, arrested, and probably sent to jail.

Original title:  I Wonder Who's Killing Her Now? (1975) AKA: Kill My Wife... Please!

Director: Steven Hilliard Stern
Writers: Mickey Rose, Jerry Cutler
Stars: Bob Dishy, Joanna Barnes, Bill Dana
Genres: Comedy, Crime

This film has many subtitle languages options available.
